############## root window #######3
# Pager
Key 1 A 4 MoveToDesk 0 0
Key 2 A 4 MoveToDesk 0 1
Key 3 A 4 MoveToDesk 0 2
Key 4 A 4 MoveToDesk 0 3

Key Right A CM GotoRightDesk
Key Left A CM GotoLeftDesk


# Minimal windows.
Key D A 4 FuncFvwmIconifyToggle
Key D A CM All (AcceptsFocus CurrentPage !Iconic !Shaded, !FvwmButtons, !"xdaliclock" !"*Desk *" !"*FvwmDocker*" !"Tild*" !"*sv*")Iconify

Key F A 4 FuncFullScreen
Key space A 4 Maximize

Key F1 A 4 Exec wcmd
Key F2 A 4 Exec devhelp
Key F3 A 4 Exec goldendict
Key F8 A 4 Module FvwmConsole
Key F12 A 4 Exec firefox
Key F11 A 4 Exec chromium --disk-cache-dir=/dev/null

Key F1 A M Menu MenuFvwmRoot
Key F12 A C Exec emacs
Key F2 A M Exec exec grun
Key F4 A M Close

Key Tab A M WindowList (CurrentPage) Root c c NoDeskSort, SelectOnRelease Meta_L,CurrentAtEnd, IconifiedAtEnd

Key r A CM Exec exec grun
Key t A MC Exec sakura

# Lock screens
Key L A 4 FuncFvwmLockScreen
Key L A CM FuncFvwmLockScreen

Key Print A N Exec exec scrot $[HOME]/tmp/root_$(date +"%Y-%m-%d_%H-%M-%S")".png"
Key Print A S Exec exec import -window $[w.id] $[HOME]/tmp/$[w.resource]_$(date +"%Y-%m-%d_%H-%M-%S")".png"
Key Print A M Exec exec import $[HOME]/tmp/$[w.resource]_p_$(date +"%Y-%m-%d_%H-%M-%S")".png"


Key t A 4 Exec exec xterm
Key Pause A C ExitMenu

Key XF86Mail A A Exec exec sylpheed
Key XF86WWW A A Exec exec xdg-open about:blank
key XF86AudioLowerVolume 	A A Exec exec amixer set Master 10%-
key XF86AudioRaiseVolume 	A A Exec exec amixer set Master 10%+
key XF86AudioMute 		A A Exec exec amixer set Master toggle
